review.reviewBody:
Used for indoor climbing so far. Comfortable when taking falls and when anchoring to the ground when belaying heavier climbers. The gear loops are a good size and there are 4 gear loops on the XS! (I wasn&apos;t sure as some harnesses don&apos;t have all the gear loops on the XS due to space). 
The harness is true to size. My waist is 26&quot; and legs 21.&quot; 
One note for improvement would be softer webbing on the leg loops or extending the padding slightly as it has pilled my mammut zinal hybrid leggings.
